{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Drop Pockets</strong> is a strategic roguelike built on top of billiards.</h2>Out on the town on a Friday night, you find yourself at a billiards bar. Folks are here from all walks of life, ready and waiting for your challenge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Billiards like never before</strong></h2>There's a lot more to Drop Pockets than just pool balls. From bowling balls to 20 sided dice, each special ball has its own unique mechanic to help, or hinder, your path to victory.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/BALLS.gif?t=1729893463\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sharks in the water</strong></h2>Pool Sharks wait at the end of every round, ready to cut your run short by applying new rules to the table. By changing physics, adding obstacles, or just flooding the table with balls, the bosses demand your best.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/BOSSES_REAL.gif?t=1729893463\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Trinkets and baubles</strong></h2>Rack up your points and get rich quick with items and upgrades. Combine dozens of Chalks, Racks, and Cues for hundreds of potential builds and ride your highs to success in Drop Pockets!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/CUES.gif?t=1729893463\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3005620?t=1729893463","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1729893463","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729893463","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729893463","categories":[{"description":"Single-pla